<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Holy Saturday</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 26, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Gracious Father,
</p>

 <p>
Holy Saturday, <br></br>
the day of waiting, <br></br>
after all of our <br></br>
hopes and dreams <br></br>
have been crushed <br></br>
by a cruel world <br></br>
and a naive idealism <br></br>
is forced to succumb <br></br>
to a harsher reality.
</p>

 <p>
But even after the <br></br>
horrors of Friday, <br></br>
the morning sun still <br></br>
rose on Saturday.
</p>

 <p>
And we have hope, <br></br>
however faint, <br></br>
however absurd.
</p>

 <p>
So we wait, <br></br>
wait to see <br></br>
what Sunday <br></br>
will bring.
</p>

 <p>
Amen
</p>


